{
  "stem": "2581.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They burned us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They shot us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They killed us in ev-- in every way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We beg our future brothers never to forget what happened here, and those that witness it-- witnessed it, to tell it to the world.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a national shrine now in Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's in the middle of nowhere, on a road where, if you don't know exactly what you're looking for, you can hardly find it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But right now, there is a lady there that she's a real righteous person, whatever religion she is.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She's a-- she wears a black dress constantly like she would be in mourning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she is so dedicated to this place, because I have a video that we send representatives from our society, from our [INAUDIBLE], from our-- people from our town from Israel, where they put up a plaque in memory of the people-- people from our town that were exterminated in such a cruel way in this place.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that is the story of Chelmno.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When  I came there the last time in '79 with the photographer, but-- because I knew I couldn't take pictures-- and a taxi driver, they had to carry me off.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's one thing to know about the place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's another thing when your feet stand on that ground.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That ground.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took the-- the ashes and threw them in River Warta.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's called 'Varta' In Polish with a 'V.' And this-- this-- these ashes are laying in this river with a hard-- with a fast current that's probably now in the Baltic Ocean.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
